These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, purple, lilac
House: art-deco, futuristic, gothic-revival
City: prague, liverpool, london
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, milk, sprite
1. the person who likes purple is between the art-deco house and the person drinking water##2
2. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the futuristic house##1
5. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
6. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Color          | yellow      | purple        | lilac     |
| House         | gothic-revival | futuristic | art-deco    |
| City   | liverpool   | prague       | london |
| Beverage         | water  | milk      | sprite    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
House: art-deco, cottage, palace
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, amber, light-blue
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, december, june
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian, american
1. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the person who likes amber is the cottage house##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the cottage house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the palace house##3
6. the palace house is in an even position##4
7. the american is between the person who likes amber and the art-deco house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| House           | cottage    | palace | art-deco |
| Color   | amber | emerald       | light-blue   |
| Birthday           | june  | december   | november     |
| Nationality         | indonesian | american       | chinese   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, rugby, cricket
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, october, november
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, azure, black
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, cola
1. the person who likes black is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
4. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person drinking cola##2
5. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
6. the person who likes black is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Sport          | cricket | sailing | rugby |
| Birthday   | november     | june | october |
| Color           | azure       | lavender   | black    |
| Beverage     | cola      | milk   | coffee |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, rabbit, turtle
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, lily, balloon-flower
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, dannemann, dunhill
House: tower, craftsman, wooden
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsiris is on the right of the wooden house##1
6. the craftsman house is on the right of the wooden house##1
7. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Pet         | rabbit  | ferret       | turtle |
| Flower           | balloon-flower     | lily      | iris   |
| Cigar   | dannemann | ritmeester | dunhill     |
| House   | tower      | wooden   | craftsman     |

