.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, wooden
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, epic, musical
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, swimming
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, motorbike
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the wooden house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| House      | wooden     | cape-cod   | farmhouse         |
| Movie-Genre           | fantasy | epic | musical |
| Sport   | swimming      | rugby   | biathlon            |
| Transport   | bus   | motorbike  | helicopter         |

