.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, blue, fuchsia
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold, zinnia
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball, cycling
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, blues, dubstep
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who likes blue##2
2. the fan of indie is the person who likes black##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is the fan of blues##1
4. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
5. the fan of indie is in an even position##4
6. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Color          | fuchsia    | black     | blue |
| Flower           | marigold | zinnia | daffodil      |
| Sport   | cycling      | volleyball       | skiing    |
| Music-Genre   | blues      | indie         | dubstep     |

