.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, weightlifting, skateboarding
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, cain, pall-mall
City: boston, new-york, san-francisco
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, fishing, singing
1. the person who's sport is handball is in the middle##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the person traveling to boston is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
7. the person who's hobby is singing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Sport          | weightlifting | handball | skateboarding |
| Cigar   | cain  | baccarat    | pall-mall |
| City   | new-york  | boston   | san-francisco    |
| Hobby     | singing   | rock-climbing       | fishing |

