The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, adventure, family
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, analyst, police-officer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, havana, baccarat
1. the police-officer is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is in an odd position##4
4. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the havana-smoker is on the left of the analyst##1
6. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4
7. the person watching disaster movies is between the analyst and the baccarat-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| City      | new-york | paris    | hamburg  |
| Movie-Genre         | family        | disaster   | adventure   |
| Job   | police-officer       | bartender    | analyst |
| Cigar     | baccarat          | havana | ritmeester       |

