.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, collecting, chess
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, green, aquamarine
3 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, whist
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, june, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
5. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person playing snooker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby      | chess       | collecting   | reading |
| Color   | emerald | aquamarine     | green |
| Game           | snooker      | scrabble | whist    |
| Birthday         | june  | february     | april |

