4. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the bolivar-smoker is in the middle##1
7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
8. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
9. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Flower           | orchid | marigold   | azalea |
