.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-18::.
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, italian, canadian
3 different pets are kept: snake, fish, chinchilla
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, cricket, lacrosse
3 different games are played: go, fish, snooker
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the owner of the chinchilla##2
3. the russian is the person playing go##1
4. the person playing fish is on the left of the italian##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
6. the italian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2        |     3      |
| Nationality      | russian         | canadian         | italian       |
| Pet         | fish          | snake        | chinchilla |
| Sport           | lacrosse | cricket | snowboarding     |
| Game   | go      | fish          | snooker     |

