.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-19::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, animation, crime
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, water
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, may, february
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, singing, writing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person watching animation movies is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre          | animation  | disaster   | crime |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | water      | soy-milk   |
| Birthday   | august     | february | may |
| Hobby         | singing | woodworking   | writing   |

