.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, fanta
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, baking, video-games
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, weightlifting, volleyball
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, chinese, canadian
1. the canadian is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the chinese is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
6. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Beverage           | mirinda  | fanta | water   |
| Hobby   | baking | video-games           | camping      |
| Sport           | volleyball   | weightlifting          | water-polo |
| Nationality     | malaysian    | canadian           | chinese |

 